@startuml
title Schema Registry + Provider (Before)
skinparam backgroundColor #FCFCFC
skinparam componentStyle rectangle
skinparam ArrowColor #4E342E
skinparam defaultFontName Consolas

actor "SDK Consumer" as Consumer #B3E5FC
component "createClient(...)" as Client #DCE775
component "from<Row>(\"table\")" as FromGeneric #FFF59D
component "Manual Row Interface" as ManualTypes #FFE082
database "Database Schema" as DbSchema #EF9A9A

Consumer --> ManualTypes : Maintain manually
ManualTypes --> FromGeneric : Pass generic
Consumer --> Client : Runtime config
Client --> FromGeneric : table string only
DbSchema ..> ManualTypes : Drift risk

note right of FromGeneric
No first-class registry object,
no introspection provider contract.
end note
@enduml
